## Doubly Linked Lists

![doubly linked](https://miro.medium.com/max/2000/1*Rkn3q6HJoEkRO4T_SVlyuw.png)



### Example Pseudo of insert

```java

// works with singly linked lists as well

new_node = Node(8) //or something

curr_node = something.HEAD

loop while True:
	if curr_node.next().data < new_node.data && curr_node.next().data != null
		curr_node = curr_node.next()
		break

new_node.next() = curr_node.next()
new_node.prev() = curr_node.address
cur_node.next().prev() = new_node.address
cur_node.next() = new_node.address


```
